-----BEGIN PGP SIGNED MESSAGE-----

This is a good way to avoid known plaintext attacks. However,
if the braiding technique is discovered, then it's back to
square one. Masking with some random data could be considered
obscurity unless special safeguards are taken to protect the
random data.

Wonderer

